definitions.definition: A longitudinal ridge or projection like the keel of a boat .
Part of a papilionaceous flower consisting of two petals , commonly united, which encloses the organs of fructification .
The keel of the breastbone of birds .
Any of several features that have a projecting central ridge

main_definition: A longitudinal ridge or projection like the keel of a boat .
secondary_definitions: ( botany ) Part of a papilionaceous flower consisting of two petals , commonly united, which encloses the organs of fructification .

( anatomy ) Any of several features that have a projecting central ridge
